11:28.021 --> 11:32.892 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But what is different, as Dmitri
said, is
taking that information and, in
the lingo

11:32.926 --> 11:37.897 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of the industry, weaponizing it,
in other
words, releasing this in public.

11:37.931 --> 11:40.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that is something we haven't
seen much
against American officials.

11:40.633 --> 11:49.642 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
