14:15.888 --> 14:20.827 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And Putin believes that
encouraged street
protests against him and his
party.

14:20.860 --> 14:23.963 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So he protested that at the
time.

14:23.996 --> 14:28.034 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
