a favor.

14:28.067 --> 14:30.837 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, I want to
ask both of
you about something.

14:30.870 --> 14:33.106 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
