14:48.721 --> 14:51.424 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DMITRI ALPEROVITCH: Well,
there's certainly
no question that there are
vulnerabilities

14:51.457 --> 14:53.326 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
