they have on
their right side is for sale.

34:05.777 --> 34:10.181 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GAYLE TZEMACH LEMMON: Jada,
whose last name
we are withholding at the
request of her lawyer,

34:10.215 --> 34:15.587 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
hadn't even started high school
when her father,
a convert to Islam, moved them
both to Jeddah

34:15.620 --> 34:17.689 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and began trying to marry her
