34:17.722 --> 34:22.661 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SHIRLEY, Aunt: She's thousands
of miles away,
and there's nothing we can do.

34:22.694 --> 34:27.132 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GAYLE TZEMACH LEMMON: Jada's
family back in
New Jersey was terrified when
